metadata.description:
Heiko discusses object representation. Luiz then presents his new finding for a touch sensor we can use in neural simulation. Ben presents the different module structures of sensors and actuators, and the problem of object segmentation.

00:00 Introduction
09:16 Object Recognition and Deformations
56:14 Touch Sensor
01:15:56 Monty Architecture
